response.overview: Documentary movie about a Ponzi scheme in Bulgaria that started as Life Insurance company and evolved into Disneyland-like Historical Park claiming to be a beacon of Bulgarian tradition, but was actually a Ponzi scheme making people take loans so they can "invest" in the scam, left with nothing but interest rates to pay, while the Scammer Ivelin Mihaylov launders money of mob leaders and lives like a king.
response.tagline: #партия величие #величие #киро брейка #киро сводника #пламен кънчев #toghether #ивелин михайлов #исторически парк
response.title: Исторически парк - Царството на Освободителя
